<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr" xmlns:v="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml" xmlns:o="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <title>Votre Réservation - Gala des PME</title>
    <style>
        body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #F8FAFC; color: #334155; font-family: 'Inter', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; width: 100% !important; height: 100% !important; }
        table { border-spacing: 0; border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; }
        td { padding: 0; }
        img { border: 0; -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic; display: block; }
        a { text-decoration: none; color: #C41230; }
        h1, h2, h3 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif; color: #0F172A; margin: 0; }
        p { margin: 0 0 16px 0; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; }
        .wrapper { width: 100%; table-layout: fixed; background-color: #F8FAFC; padding-bottom: 40px; }
        .container { width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #FFFFFF; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
        .header { background-color: #0F172A; padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center; background-image: url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/cubes.png'); }
        .content { padding: 40px 40px; }
        .footer { background-color: #0F172A; padding: 30px 20px; text-align: center; color: #94A3B8; font-size: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
        .button { display: inline-block; background-color: #C41230; color: #FFFFFF !important; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 50px; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 20px; text-decoration: none; }
        .info-table { width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px; border-collapse: collapse; }
        .info-table td { padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #F1F5F9; font-size: 14px; color: #334155; }
        .info-label { font-weight: bold; color: #64748B; width: 40%; }
        .info-value { color: #0F172A; font-weight: 600; text-align: right; }
        .ticket-card { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F172A 0%, #1E293B 100%); color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; margin: 20px 0; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #D4AF37; }
        .ticket-type { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 24px; color: #D4AF37; margin-bottom: 5px; }
        .ticket-price { font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; }
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .content { padding: 25px 20px; }
            h1 { font-size: 24px !important; }
            .container { width: 100% !important; border-radius: 0; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <table role="presentation" class="container" align="center">
            <tr>
                <td class="header">
                    <img src="logo.png" alt="Gala des PME" width="120" style="margin: 0 auto; display: block;" />
                    <div style="margin-top: 15px; height: 1px; width: 40px; background-color: #C41230; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"></div>
                    <p style="color: #D4AF37; font-size: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 3px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0;">L'Excellence Entrepreneuriale</p>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="content">
                    <h1 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #C41230;">Réservation Confirmée</h1>
                    <p style="text-align: center; color: #64748B; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 30px;">Réf: RGPME{{reservation.id}}</p>
                    
                    <p>Bonjour <strong>{{reservation.fullname}}</strong>,</p>
                    
                    <p>Merci de votre réservation pour la soirée de l'excellence. Nous avons bien enregistré votre commande de billets pour le Gala des PME 2026.</p>
                    
                    <div class="ticket-card">
                        <div class="ticket-type">{{reservation.typeTicket.label}}</div>
                        <div class="ticket-price">{{reservation.quantity}} x {{reservation.typeTicket.tarif | number_format(0, ',', ' ')}}</div>
                        <div style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12px; color: #94A3B8;">Total à régler : <span style="color: white; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px;">{{reservation.total | number_format(0, ',', ' ')}}</span></div>
                    </div>

                    <div style="background-color: #F8FAFC; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 30px 0;">
                        <h3 style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 15px; border-bottom: 2px solid #E2E8F0; padding-bottom: 10px;">Détails</h3>
                        <table class="info-table">
                            <tr>
                                <td class="info-label">Nom</td>
                                <td class="info-value">{{reservation.fullname}}</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td class="info-label">Email</td>
                                <td class="info-value">{{reservation.email}}</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td class="info-label">Téléphone</td>
                                <td class="info-value">{{reservation.telephone}}</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td class="info-label">Fonction</td>
                                <td class="info-value">{{reservation.fonction}}</td>
                            </tr>
                        </table>
                    </div>

                    <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; color: #64748B;">
                        Un conseiller commercial vous contactera sous 24h au <strong>{{reservation.telephone}}</strong> pour finaliser le paiement (Mobile Money ou Virement) et organiser la remise de vos billets.
                    </p>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="footer">
                    <p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: #FFFFFF; font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 16px;">Gala des PME 2026</p>
                    <p>Sofitel Abidjan Hôtel Ivoire • Boulevard Hassan II</p>
                    <p><a href="tel:+2252722482626" style="color: #94A3B8; text-decoration: none;">+225 27 22 48 26 26</a> • <a href="mailto:billetterie@galadespme.com" style="color: #94A3B8; text-decoration: none;">billetterie@galadespme.com</a></p>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
